name: Jade Fever
overview: A reality show following a family-owned mining company drilling for jade in the B.C., Canada.

episodes.name: Head start
episodes.overview: Funding her mining season alone and determined to start her hunt for jade a month early, Claudia is forced to rethink her strategy when snow and high water stops the crews in their tracks.

episodes.name: Hard Core
episodes.overview: Robin follows a hunch to a new site at an old claim; Josh's high expectations and short fuse test Gary's patience.

episodes.name: Tip Of The Iceberg
episodes.overview: Guy struggles with the excavator to expose a massive find; Josh's dissatisfaction with his position in the crew causes family conflicts to boil over.

episodes.name: You're My Boy Blue
episodes.overview: The crew faces a dangerous recovery on the banks above the Turnagain River; Guy and Gary continue to stumble over jade at Dynasty; Josh searches around Jade City for his missing dog.

episodes.name: Uphill Battle
episodes.overview: Cutting a potential million-dollar find is put on hold when old equipment fails; a new saw could reveal an unexpected windfall from a decades-old family heirloom.

episodes.name: All Slice, No Dice
episodes.overview: Cutting finally starts on the giant jade lens at Dynasty, but big fractures slice off the lens; the Jade City community is on edge when two trucks roll over on the same stretch of highway.

episodes.name: Slipping Away
episodes.overview: Downpours threaten the crew's safety and shut down mining at Pit 3; Josh gets a chance to prove himself on the excavator, but a breakdown tests his patience.

episodes.name: Failing Grade
episodes.overview: When an important jade buyer isn't impressed with the Pit 3 lens, Claudia is forced to make a difficult decision that disappoints her crew.

episodes.name: Moving Day
episodes.overview: The race to pack up camp at Wolverine becomes a nightmare when heat, sickness and a forest fire descend on the crew.

episodes.name: Battered And Bruised
episodes.overview: The brutal trek to a new mine site separates the family and pushes Josh to his breaking point; scrappy Larry struggles to keep his extra-wide army truck on the steep and narrow road.

episodes.name: The Curse Of Wolverine
episodes.overview: Claudia chomps at the bit to break ground on the new site, but progress is stalled by a series of unlucky incidents at their old mining camp, Wolverine.

episodes.name: Shower Day
episodes.overview: Small luxuries in camp cheer up a disgruntled crew, and surprise visitors raise Claudia's hopes for her future at 2 Mile.

episodes.name: Medio-Core
episodes.overview: Gary and Josh fail to return from a routine fuel run; drill cores cast doubt over the quality of jade lenses at 2 Mile.

episodes.name: We Found Jade
episodes.overview: The crew finally hits it big, but with winter descending, Claudia worries that the big find may have come too late.

episodes.name: The Long and Grinding Road
episodes.overview: Claudia is desperate to start mining, but brutal road conditions have her questioning whether the crew will even make it into their claim.

episodes.name: Nose for Jade
episodes.overview: While Guy and Gary race to fix the torn-up road into the claim, Claudia's hoping a new crew member will be the lucky ticket she desperately needs to turn this make-or-break mining season into a success.

episodes.name: Bunkhouse Blues
episodes.overview: Robin's surprise shopping spree stresses Claudia out when his purchasing blunders delay their mining season. Scrappy Larry shares some unexpected news of his own.

episodes.name: Stuck in the Middle
episodes.overview: Claudia tries to keep the peace when Robin and her Dad butt heads, while the crew struggle to fix one problem after another on their mine truck.

episodes.name: It's My Party
episodes.overview: Gary and Josh are frustrated by a series of breakdowns, while Claudia makes a shocking announcement that derails Robin's plans and causes conflict between the couple.

episodes.name: Who's the Boss
episodes.overview: Tensions boil over between Robin, Josh and Steve about how to mine and when Claudia steps in, things get downright explosive.

episodes.name: Running on Empty
episodes.overview: Plagued with truck troubles, Robin and his crew race to get a fuel run done before the equipment runs dry. Claudia hires Scrappy Larry to clean up the Jade City yard but he makes a bigger mess.

episodes.name: Ridge to Riches
episodes.overview: Robin clashes with Claudia and Josh over the quality of jade coming out of their pit, while Larry's attempt to help get the crew bunkhouse to camp goes sideways.

episodes.name: Bunkhouse or Bust
episodes.overview: Bad brakes, frazzled nerves and a rough road have Claudia doubting her crew can haul their huge bunkhouse to camp in one piece.

episodes.name: Playing with Fire
episodes.overview: Claudia and crew are determined to keep mining despite wildfires burning around their claim, until things take a turn for the worse and they have to race to get out.

episodes.name: Risky Business
episodes.overview: After losing two weeks of mining to the wildfires, Claudia and Robin take the risk of returning to Two Mile and gamble on the opening of a new pit. Scrappy Larry heads into the burned area in hopes of rescuing his abandoned skidder.

episodes.name: No Country for Cold Men
episodes.overview: Claudia gets stressed out trying to get their best jade ready for buyers, while her crew's morale is tested as they battle the cold to finally start cutting the 90-tonne boulder.

episodes.name: Snow Job
episodes.overview: Claudia pulls out all the stops to try and make a big sale to jade buyers, while up at the mine Guy and Gary struggle through the first snowstorm of the season.

episodes.name: Pushing the Limits
episodes.overview: Claudia pushes her crew to keep mining despite freezing temperatures and deteriorating road conditions, but her biggest obstacle could be Robin who wants to pack up before it's too late.

episodes.name: Between A Truck And A Hard Place
